    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nre: https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/pull/3690\n\nNvim/Vim has `shellescape()`, but that is specific to 'shell', while `vim.fn.glob()` is not(?).\n\nAnd `vim.glob` isn't exactly equivalent to \"Vim glob\", so `vim.glob.to_lpeg(vim.pesc(...))` may not be 100% correct?\n\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nDo we need `globescape()`?\n\nOr we need to document guidance on replacing `vim.fn.glob()` with `vim.fs` + `vim.glob`.",
